The config.ini file contains all the properties of the vehicle and the time line

The vehicles should be defined at 2. Example definitions are given.

'start_sim' starts the simulation.

'sim.cpp' contains the terminal version.
'final.cpp' contains the opengl version.
 

The code only needs to be compiled and runned.

Compile command line for terminal version : "g++ sim.cpp"
Run command line for terminal version : "./a.out"

Compile command line for opengl version : "g++ final.cpp -lGL -lGLU -lglut"
Run command line for opengl verison : "./a.out"